{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"丽纯Doris","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKCwvBZwhCYLm35INJvTwIAHyjufNrN1pAL0RtRyNoUqaSQMcwU3TmWEQ4lSSEeRZC1ic89HicRVK0l3pBOVEOAKL/0","content":"为什么写作要列提纲，再填充内容?","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9003,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492777330000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"蓝田","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQP84V0Q7no8ZeAnVwrJSfJym1ZsqjCpPdYn5sq6UYuNcpPuNzXibVh6UYOk6ibnJxNNPICFIxTV10ia/0","content":"先掌握思维方式在学习具体知识，可以得到事半功倍的效果，从术的层面讲，就是利用较好的思考方式学习知识，使知识了解更加全面、有结构、有层次、且透彻，利于转化为自我知识资产。好比上学读书前的自我预习，看书先看目录。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8988,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492774787000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"大雯雯","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay2Kff44yTDy2feiacIoc1nfjG7DPb0YSmpC66IerPKJEGJOQz0YSzS4RL1kQbYskY3CoEbCeTgtg8/0","content":"<p>先有个筐再去收玉米XD～因为我小时候我妈老是跟我讲，大狗熊掰玉米，掰一个掉一个，最后掰一路，手里只有最后一个～</p><p>没有筐，掰下来的玉米只能在手里捧着，很容易掉；而且也拿不多，羡慕人家手大拿的多，把自己拿不多甩锅给自己手小，其实人类嘛，手再大再小能差多少，都是一个物种，傻蛋啊，人家不是手大，人家有筐啊有筐；并且觉得很累，很费劲，掰的过程很烦很不爽。</p><p>同理，没有思维方式，具体知识全靠记忆力，短期记忆很难转化为长期或永久记忆，很容易遗忘；而且也学不多，没学多少呢就觉得学不动了，以为是自己智商有问题，其实是因为没有思维方式；学的时候觉得很吃力，很烦，就破罐子破摔不学了。</p><p>筐又分很多种，手提的、背着的、带轮子的、能把玉米分类放置的、全自动化的</p><p>思维方式也分厉害的和不厉害的，很少有人一点点儿思维方式都没有，在现有思维方式基础上不断升级也很关键。</p><p>此外，摘玉米的筐和打渔的筐可能不一样。</p><p>所以学习不同类型具体知识，思维方式也有可能不同吧。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8981,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492773914000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小小云","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjOkia7eibkITySvUExH5dicgdSdEHl6Y1FLwVWDq7XOjt0EbfuA0EIVRVGCgKLzyU1mIhTtk3AYMl8R/0","content":"是先了解交通规则和车子性能在上路开车实践？ 是先了解对方的基本状况在考虑结婚？ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 是先让小孩适应小学的行为习惯还是上小学在培养？ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 类比问题能够提供清晰的思路，类比问题能够更清晰看到前因后果","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7932,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492487137000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"青青枣实～","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/UPj0egwhddG46evSjhoopsDOglJ7YDNJTysd8ZXpLppVibia3UjtV3rAsibHvE3RxfbTrxP1BIFxdRpR6LrLPUahp0GibZUNPGy6/0","content":"良好的思维方式让个人学习地更加高效，对知识点的理解更透彻，有逻辑性地进行归纳吸收。<div><br></div><div>个人的思维学习与人际交往能力提升</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7905,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492442594000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"影子（one life one liver）","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay7P6qrmu6EFgMxv9yByicqqSVMrdaJoMs4TEyich23rD3ictMbhBfngbwia0x0G3qzXEM5ib5SQ8bx5vQ/0","content":"<div>为什么磨刀不误砍柴工呢？</div><div>为什么知道挤某个螺丝值999元，而挤螺丝只要一块钱？</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7766,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492267140000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"JO","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibbafiaiamMCT1NibWJvqonUP8wpgyMv9VFbibW13z23eLGopaoFebhOC3eueQYWpbuP5Oz15Az5R3JY/0","content":"<p>类比：用渔具钓鱼。盲目抓鱼效率不高，也很有可能白忙一阵，所以好的渔具，比如鱼竿、渔网等捕捞的手段会效率高得多。</p><p>所以，学习知识也是一样，举个结构化思维的例子，现在知识的获取非常便捷，我们常有朋友圈看文章的经验，这篇很有道理，那一篇也很好，但其实常常是读了很多，忘了很多，对生活学习产生的作用非常有限。</p><p>不过，如果可以用结构化思维，把文章拆解，就会对文章的理解更深入，也容易记忆。特别是，将里面的知识归结到自己已有的知识脉络中去，那么这个知识可以内化成自己的能力了。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7564,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491958191000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FZibDrTsS1osmryDqKeuAvlF9licJ4nKDicnJ1HjwXTbvxdlVJj5oBJgqhR72iaGMxLcib1jJGsyWnUnj/0","content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">思维方式具有普适性，一种方式可以跨学科、可以应用到多种场景。相比<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">学习具体知识，学习并<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">掌握思维方式更省力、更能帮助我们看清事物的本质和事物间的联系，进而更有效的解决问题。</span></span>因此，我们应先<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">掌握</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">思维方式，再学习<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">具体知识</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">，锻炼自己的</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.6000003814697px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;\">举一反三的能力</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; line-height: 28px;\">。</span></span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">生活中 ，可以类比的知识有很多。</span>比如金字塔原理，和道家的\"<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">道生一，一生二，二生三，三生万物\"不谋而合。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">比如大数据的思想运用到体育比赛中，可以精准的预测比赛结果、判断选手竞技水平。{此例有争议}。比如任务型矩阵模型，可以应用的地方就更多了。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px;\">当我们遇到新生事物或者刚出现的难题{此表述不恰当}时，不妨</span>像新东方名师朱伟所说：”不要强求不可知，要用已知推未知。“</span></span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7207,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491317212000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"易\uD83D\uDC33\uD83C\uDF3B","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-27","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEJaNibebib7zYA7govclzibRvDicvMBW4xSgvNSoU6BnkPG64LGzxicl76E77GIRnicAYibTyAOgicguJZqnA/0","content":"1.为什么写文章要先列提纲再填充内容，\n2.为什么素描写生要先画框架，再勾勒细节..\n3.为什么建房子要先打地基建房梁再到筑墙，","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6063,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490613481000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"文","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-27","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEuUJBibwaegwqwa7rXILx7WPapDW7tTnawmINtpCLZRonooMm0ezL1xuuMLrs1trOmgp0gmOpYOuk/0","content":"为什么要“先考试理论知识再学习如何开车？”\n为什么要“先看完说明书再学习如何摄影？”\n掌握了正确的方法才能够顺利完成一件事情","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6079,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490613273000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"肖竹","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-26","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLD59UCXXaKTUtCEG9o0icohtHzK8T6MNlTKeyIANBf0tBvzpDtzbWvYOGa2wgDvGdG6k1pCFiafpDjg/0","content":"写作前先列提纲，再动手细写。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5785,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490499441000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"绢子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny69WHp8icWIITPaUXDQLv58bjzBbkuVforicx3Pn6ibBpshvnyic56N783Pu1bibMnrvVukb81QfBIeqgAbM4TmCdcFKo/0","content":"先掌握思维方式再学习具体知识，就如同建高楼，基础楼体结构先建起来，再按照不同的户型设计填充墙体窗户等。这种建设方式效率很高，基础框架搭好，填充速度就很快了；同样，思维方式也是学习的基础，它能促进理解，理解力上去了学习效率就会更高。\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5259,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490260757000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张YY","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLDC88nCjl5mticEwn6d95CyLS2K9XiaEIPB6n8icXpxKiaNZlVIVbTBj7XJVOQvkuoOHDzbycbc5YU9tA/0","content":"就像为什么先画好建筑图纸再考虑房子具体怎么建造","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4034,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490103369000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Evelyn","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEK5ydEXl1eL0s4u0whsKzicBua4A2LJEoY90AsCUsNMcmGpFv0UEA2SJpPP58oSPiahTuwHtAk8G0RA/0","content":"先掌握思维方式再学习具体知识？\n类比为建筑一栋楼房，先搭好基础框架后再填充各层水泥砖瓦材料？\n回答：思维方式是最根本的学习方法，类比为建筑一栋楼房，就是说我们要从最基本的方法框架学起来，这个是核心基础，只有在搭建起来框架后，再填充其余的水泥，砖瓦（所需知识）也就有所支撑和依据，搭建起来的房屋也最为牢固。否则，如果只是单纯想到哪儿就往哪儿块构建，则经不住任何风雨的考量，容易坍塌。","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4419,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489980555000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"博学笃志","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjGcyXgjKvljRv5hsGdS0pUiaecGsLTmju6ib8JdHpQwqZqXeovGLB8HRWVxBjq0BaZpicsLFdj3dfibia/0","content":"先提升元认知能力再提升具体能力。\n射人先射马，擒贼先擒王。\n提高内部深层次认知，掌握通用规律，学习具体知识，可以举一反三，提高学习效率。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4093,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489847201000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"盛夏tl","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQLZSOLpBibDcibZ6sFXGjaugXibNJwMAvZF35uJNo0TzNd8uGdLrfymhDiav0qNFFCZzEIQIxyrWNEPw/0","content":"种子是要先种植才能发芽吗？\n结论是阶段性去思考问题去学习和掌握问题背后的问题。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3929,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489802561000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小丸子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEvvp5NNEFv62t7fe0CbsQeFk2FkhAsd2cicrNctjzgrcB9ZXeibiadGqIic69guhPrE7ibo41khAyUYoa/0","content":"为什么磨刀不误砍柴工？\n做事情之前做好准备才能做得更好更高效\n为什么要先上学之后在工作呢？\n做事情之前需要具备能完成事情的基础能力，不然往往做不成功\n\n为什么要先学习人体构造然后再学做外科手术呢？\n手再灵活下错刀也不是名医，做好一件事情要了解他的必要前提\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3589,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489746640000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"原问题：先掌握思维方式再学习具体知识\n类比问题：\n先看菜谱再做菜\n先看游泳视频再去学游泳。\n\n先了解未知事物的大致运作状态---比标实践--纠错--再实践--达到理想状态\n\n思维方式就像是事物的基础运作规律和原则，一开始了解思维方式也只是文字上的了解，等到做了，重复做，思考后，才会有更深层次的认识。但是一开始就直接去学知识，就容易迷失在知识的海洋里，没有整体的框架，对事物没有全局的认识。\n\n\n","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3555,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489734304000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Claudia\uD83C\uDF88孙雪","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQHEGlNicG6ucZIjY65zAdPsmz39B6Cc3Eib47zwsibAicbBofwLZ9giaYlG5FlJSSKovICibSd49qaEFyI/0","content":"先搭好房屋的架子，再往上添砖加瓦；\n先知道如何阅读再去读书；\n先看操作说明书再去组装电器。\n\n得出的结论是磨刀不误砍柴工。好的方法论或者思路可以事半功倍。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3039,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489392551000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Demi","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-02","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98Vq5XRcAhicEkcf1lPhk0C2xpXzlUtFibNPIuKxvprX27YITluDA1cuazfKnOFcchructkay0UkLX6egVqQJqN7N5/0","content":"不会飞，先会走？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":2391,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1488415293000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
